<br>
So, they only have a few options:<br>
1. Make charm so you can swarm kite but not get better xp than grouping (ie, very low level charm).  Its already like this and a lot of bards want a higher level charm.<br>
<br>
2. Completely get rid of charm for bards.  That would only make SoE happy.<br>
<br>
3. Make a high level charm where you can swarm kite and gain xp faster than any group XP.  Half the bards would be happy about this, all other classes would be unhappy and SoE would be unhappy.<br>
<br>
4. Make a charm spell which makes swarm kiting very difficult, but is still a usable tool in CC situations.  I believe that is what they are trying to acomplish. <p><center>
